body.description: The perfect foundation for fun and learning, the Delta Children MySize Table & 2 Chairs Set features a smooth, wood top that make it extremely durable and easy to clean. Whether your child uses it for art projects, tea parties, snack time or homework, this kids play table and chair set will enhance their sense of wonder no matter what activity they use it for. Sized just right for your growing child, the Delta Children MySize Table & 2 Chairs Set will provide years of creative fun. The table's beautiful finish will complement existing bedroom, playroom or living room decor, easily allowing you to create a space that works for kids and adults alike. Available in a number of beautiful colors. Coordinates with other items in the Delta Children MySize Collection. MYSIZE Trademark Used With Permission. Delta Children was founded around the idea of making safe, high-quality children's furniture affordable for all families. They know there's nothing more important than safety when it comes to your child's space. That's why all Delta Children products are built with long-lasting materials to ensure they stand up to years of jumping and playing. Plus, they are rigorously tested to meet or exceed all industry safety standards.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for the younger crowd
reviews.reviewText: This table set is great for our younger grandkids. It was very easy to put together and very durable. The price point was also very attractive.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Installation is important!!
reviews.reviewText: I wish amazon let you reply to comments because i have seen so many pictures of incorrect installation saying that it is not sturdy or they have to tighten down the screws. CHECK YOUR INSTALLATION AND LOOK AT THE PRODUCT PICTURE FOR REFERENCE. bought this item over a year ago and the only problem I have had with it is the paint discoloration. Wiping it down daily definitely strips the paint. Other than that it's super incredible sturdy. It has held up for over a year, no cracks, not wobbly, haven't had to tighten anything down. Definitely worth it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Toddler Table
reviews.reviewText: This table is perfect for toddlers. It is well made, sturdy, nice quality, and looks nice. Would definitely recommend this for any toddler.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect size and sturdy!
reviews.reviewText: I bought this table and chairs for my 4 year old granddaughter! In her words, “this is the perfect table! I can do crafts, read a book, draw and even eat dinner on it!” One of the pieces arrived slightly damaged, but after contacting the manufacturer, it was replaced. (Not the easiest process to get a replacement part, but my persistence paid off!). I would highly recommend this product!

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good for the price
reviews.reviewText: Perfect little table for the kids to do activities, eat, etc. it’s pretty easy to install, took about 30 total. The only downside is that it doesn’t seem very durable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Easy to put together and looks so nice. My toddler loves it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Bought this for an absolute little terror of a boy & it holding up to rough use. His Mom also has sat on the chair with no problem. Just bought a second one to be used with his kitchen set in the kitchen. The first is in the living room. The price is a bargain & it is very easy to put together.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Stood up against it all!
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this set in 2021 for my then 2 & 3yr old girls. My intention was to get something study that would last a while. It has exceeded my expectations and we still use it to this day. If you have toddlers you know they’re not exactly careful with their items! My girls have used this daily since it was delivered. It’s served as a meal table 3X a day, a craft table, coloring table, and then some. They have leaned back in the chairs, toted them around the house to climb, used them to help mommy with dishes and chores, as well as a podium to stand and sing on! I’m back 2yrs later to purchase again as one of the chairs finally gave away. Please do not let this detour you, this chair has survived more than most over its 2yrs in my home.Pros:-Sturdy as heck, my 3yr old thinks she’s Spider-Man and this chair has been her favorite crime fighting tool.-Easy to clean and forgiving of stains; I’ve cleaned it with soap and water multiple times a day everyday and it’s barely faded in a few spots.-Perfect size; I was worried it would be too small as my girls got older. My 5yr old is 64lbs and it’s still very comfortable and convenient for her. We’ve used it since my youngest daughter was almost 2yrs and it was never too large.Color and style- It’s a nice neutral color, obviously made for children, but is not flimsy and colorful drawing a lot of attention. I guess what I’m trying to say is; it sits in my living room and isn’t a site for sore eyes. It looks nice in the room and ties well with our other furniture.We love it and definitely recommend it!

Very well constructed and easy to put together. My toddler has climbed all over the table and chairs and they are very sturdy. Looks exactly like the pictures. We did a lot of shopping around before buying, and we’re happy we went with this one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on January 2, 2019
reviews.reviewText: Beautiful little table and chairs sits in our kitchen with pride
The perfect little table for kids, great price and quality! Was exactly as pictured and what we were looking for.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on February 1, 2019
reviews.reviewText: Absolutely amazing product so happy with it!

reviews.reviewTitle: Love this table. A great buy!!
reviews.reviewText: Despite all the negative reviews about this table arriving damaged, I decided to purchase it anyway and trust the positive reviews. So glad that I did!!! This table is perfect for our 18 month old. It has zero damage on it, and she LOVES eating her meals at her new table. It was simple to install, and our daughter even “helped” us assemble it. It has been a perfect fit for our home and I am very happy with this product. It does get fingerprints on it easily but hey, what do you expect with a kids product?
